summary: This mod adds many useful starting items to the room behind Farengars HQ. It will definetly help in the beggining of the game and is great but not overpowered. Bye love you guys!
descriptionHtml: I always was kind of bare in the beginning of the game and I\'ve always been longing for a decent set of armor in the beginning of the game. So I made this mod. It adds about 150 gold a ebony sword and mace, A enchanted necklace, Full set of steel plate armor, Dwarven shield, Smithing ingredients, And Alchemy ingredients. Please be gracious this is my first mod.
author: Willstick
